  03 Aug 2013; James Rowe <jnrowe@gmail.com> jnrowe-pypi.eclass:
  Use https for PyPI links.

  14 Jun 2013; James Rowe <jnrowe@gmail.com> jnrowe-github.eclass:
  Minor grammar fix.

