  10 Jan 2010; James Rowe <jnrowe@gmail.com> jnrowe-pypi.eclass: [479: Fixed]
  Support MY_PN in jnrowe-pypi.eclass.

  18 Oct 2009; James Rowe <jnrowe@gmail.com> jnrowe-pypi.eclass: [68d: Fixed]
  Added module_script_wrapper function to pypi eclass.  The main purpose of this
  function is to create wrapper scripts for modules, in the same
  vein as setuptools entry points but allowing us to remove setuptools from
  RDEPEND.

  14 Oct 2009; James Rowe <jnrowe@gmail.com> jnrowe-pypi.eclass: [680: Fixed]
  Added initial jnrowe-pypi eclass.  Switched potential users over to the new
  eclass.
